page.title: 13Fashion in Fremington
page.content: Being smartly dressed is very important to a lot of people, especialy mums.Denims are reasonably popular with children.The best dressed television presenters are thought to be Terry Wogan and Jan Leeming.The wost dressed television presenters are Frank Bough and Carol Barnes.Boy George,by coincidence,is the most liked and disliked pop star,and is the lead singer of the most liked pop group,culture club.Princess Diana is the best dressed member of the Royal Family and Prince Charles the worst.Nearly all ear ring wearers wear them always.The most commonly worn piece jewelery is a ring.Hair spray is used by about 50% of the population at home although its not commonly used at other events.The idea of colouring hair is not very popular.
